cs.SI, cs.CY, cs.DC, cs.NI, cs.CR 

The paper discusses the Social Internet of Things (SIoT) and its integration with new computing models. It focuses on the challenges of IoT and how SIoT can overcome them by taking inspiration from social computing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Other likely categories include cs.CY (Computers and Society), cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
